Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.13,0:00:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,After consuming all six of your books and many CDs,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.30,0:00:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,my intention is to produce consciousness music
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.50,0:00:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that's beneficial and uplifting for mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.12,0:00:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Bach and Brahms and Beethoven all knew they were writing for God,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.68,0:00:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and they all produced music that calibrated over 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,By all accounts, they were kind of grumpy men.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.34,0:00:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So my question is, do you have any tips?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.78,0:00:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So even if I'm not calibrating over 500,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.71,0:00:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,how would one produce music or works?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.16,0:00:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You uplift mankind by that which you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.54,0:00:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and that which you are then finds multiple modes of expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.10,0:00:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,With you, it's music.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.92,0:00:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,With me, it's teaching and doing research.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.06,0:00:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But each of those is our own way
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.14,0:00:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of calibrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.64,0:01:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to serve God and serve our fellow man,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.14,0:01:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and by doing so, also serve our own inner self,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.22,0:01:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,with a capital S.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.42,0:01:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sign right there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.10,0:01:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So your intention is what sets the energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Your intention is what sets the energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.92,0:01:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and it then is a consequence of that which you have become,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.62,0:01:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that which you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.19,0:01:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That which you are expresses itself in your music.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.89,0:01:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There are people,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.91,0:01:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,who's personalities were isolated from their muse, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.43,0:01:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They were expressing their muse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.39,0:01:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're asking is that your muse
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.61,0:01:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and yourself be one in the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.56,0:02:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.30,0:02:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a noble intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.21,0:02:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, can I get a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.26,0:02:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes you don't please people,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.70,0:02:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,even though you do that, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.38,0:02:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And everybody likes Kowalewski, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.76,0:02:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a birthday tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.51,0:02:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mozart's birthday is tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.86,0:02:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody said to me, Mozart who?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.76,0:02:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.26,0:02:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's Denise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a spiritual group where I live.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.76,0:02:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been doing your practices and listening to your information.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.21,0:03:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm getting those strange energetic surges
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.56,0:03:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and some kind of convulsion type things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.56,0:03:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And I mostly just think, okay, you know, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.15,0:03:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They're getting a little out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.55,0:03:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, slow down the spiritual work then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.55,0:03:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Slow it down a bit until you catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.30,0:03:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you have to take periods of rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.01,0:03:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, even in a monastery where they pray many hours a day,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,they take off times and go out and do gardening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.01,0:03:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, gardening is classically done in monasteries
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.01,0:03:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,because otherwise you dry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They say you dry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You dry up and you start becoming mechanical, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.94,0:04:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So in a monastery, they pray and they meditate
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.54,0:04:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and then they go out and garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.54,0:04:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So you need more gardening, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.54,0:04:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.70,0:04:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.28,0:04:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So when these things get out of hand, then just?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you mean by things getting out of hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.28,0:04:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the United States government or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you mean by convulsion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.38,0:04:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I just have, I do have the surges and occasionally I'll just kind of do a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you what to do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a Diet Pepsi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a sacred drink, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:05:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now they have it with ginseng so it's even more sacred.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hokens.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's Karen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.96,0:05:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come from Australia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I just felt a really strong pull to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.96,0:05:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She has to speak closer to the mic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She's from Australia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from Australia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt a really strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's why I can't hear her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She's talking more from Australia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Funny accent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt a really strong pull to come here to see you and I wanted to thank you for all
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.96,0:05:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.96,0:05:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.96,0:05:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was thinking about that last night, how precious your work is to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.96,0:05:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She has to be closer to the microphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.96,0:05:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.96,0:05:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking last night how precious your work is to me and how passionate I am and
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,all of a sudden this fear rose up that what if I leave this body and come back again another
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,body and I've never heard of Dr. Hokens.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what she's asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.96,0:05:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She says what if she, she has this fear and it came up in her head.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Of what if she left this body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.41,0:05:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And didn't get a chance to hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.41,0:05:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can hear me on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.41,0:05:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on channel 18 on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.41,0:06:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is if I came back in another body, would I still have all that you've taught
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I just fear that because your work is so precious to me, if I came back in another body, would
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, your intention, your intention then prevails.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Your intention plus your karmic propensities prevail, prevail.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And you said before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.08,0:06:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to be thrust someplace that's improper against your will.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.08,0:06:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.08,0:06:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,God looks after his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's summertime down there, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to get him to Australia someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a beautiful country.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.88,0:06:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.58,0:06:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.58,0:06:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Lord, give me a mercer these bands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.50,0:06:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:07:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.14,0:07:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.14,0:07:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.14,0:07:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.34,0:07:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.34,0:07:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.54,0:07:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.34,0:07:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.34,0:07:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.82,0:07:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.82,0:07:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mercedes bands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.82,0:07:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.26,0:07:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to see you in September.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.82,0:07:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the first time, and I'm in two groups in Boulder studying your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, I went to see the Buddha relics, and since I've seen you, all the shit has
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.19,0:07:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,hit the fan, karmically.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and I heard what you said to the other person about slow down, but I don't
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.18,0:07:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,want to slow down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.18,0:07:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then don't complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.18,0:07:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you're saying how can I eat too much
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.23,0:07:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and not feel full
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.39,0:08:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,now if you're driven
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritually driven
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,then there's certain side effects
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.18,0:08:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,from being spiritually driven
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the question I had
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.08,0:08:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,for you is I'm in a
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Course in Miracles group and a lot of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,people in the Course in Miracles
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.40,0:08:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,group start talking
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.32,0:08:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,about that once they're into
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,forgiveness that they no longer have
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.08,0:08:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,personal karma
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.86,0:08:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,there's lots of other karmas besides
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.26,0:08:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,forgiveness
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,guilt is not the only
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.48,0:08:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,determinant of karma
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that would be true if guilt was
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.44,0:08:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the only one it's not the only one
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.06,0:08:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,multiple determinants of karma
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.03,0:08:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,every thought every action
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,every choice determines karma
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,is there any impact
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,with forgiveness on karma
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.41,0:08:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,of course
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.71,0:08:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.37,0:08:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.69,0:08:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.71,0:08:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but the Course in Miracles is not the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.71,0:08:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,be-all and end-all
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.09,0:09:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you know it calibrates
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,around 550
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.51,0:09:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's good
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's not the most overwhelming
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,12 step groups calibrate higher than that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.03,0:09:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.59,0:09:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,workbook itself
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates 600
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.21,0:09:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the main
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.59,0:09:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,big book calibrates around 550
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.59,0:09:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.73,0:09:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,it loosens you to the degree
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.93,0:09:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that guilt is holding you down but there's lots of things
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.05,0:09:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that are holding you down besides guilt
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.96,0:09:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,hi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,a question has puzzled me for a long time
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.08,0:09:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that is
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I could be in a specific
