Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.14,0:16:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.54,0:16:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, my name's Phil, I'm from Sacramento.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.14,0:16:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a Course in Miracles student and a student of Tara Singh,
