Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and I now have time to devote more time to spiritual things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the past, something's always kind of showed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, like the Course and, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.52,0:16:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and even coming here just kind of happened, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.34,0:16:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It sort of showed up for me, but now things seem
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.80,0:16:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to be kind of stagnated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.63,0:16:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And my question is, I guess.
