Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.37,0:16:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems to have kind of slowed down as far as stuff showing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean, in a sense like that.
