Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Crying you cry alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.37,0:21:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.75,0:21:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Laughter is the quickest way to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.85,0:21:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I do a solitary kinesiology test?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How can what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.85,0:21:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A solitary kinesiology test.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.03,0:21:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.55,0:21:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the O-ring finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Or any finger, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the O-ring finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.24,0:21:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to break the strength of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.70,0:21:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I say the simplest way is take a stack of books
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.04,0:21:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and you'll find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.78,0:21:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You hold Jesus Christ in your mind and you lift the books.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you hold Bin Laden in mind and you pick the books.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.86,0:21:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's very obvious which one is above 200
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.16,0:21:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and which is below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.36,0:21:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And would anything develop with practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is it kind of just like you automatically know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.85,0:21:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Both go out at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.23,0:21:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,On the one hand, intuitively you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.81,0:21:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And secondly, you learn from practice also.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.59,0:21:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Like anything, you get better with practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.56,0:21:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.06,0:21:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of people have different techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.44,0:21:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, some people will fall forward with a yes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.74,0:21:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and backward with a no, using the whole body as a pendulum.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.06,0:22:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can, you know, whatever is attractive to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.94,0:22:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and you find that it's useful, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.76,0:22:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.60,0:22:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people, they use their fingernail like if it's a no,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.76,0:22:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll hang up and they pull it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.82,0:22:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's a yes, it'll be smoother.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.32,0:22:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's a lot of different techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.44,0:22:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything that tests muscle strength, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.48,0:22:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,muscle strength, comparative muscle strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.13,0:22:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.04,0:22:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.24,0:22:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. Sri Ranji heads the Oneness Movement
