Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.54,0:23:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oneness, a Oneness Movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.20,0:23:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not familiar with the Oneness Movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.26,0:23:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
