Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.54,0:24:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.84,0:24:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think that's my answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.25,0:24:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.07,0:24:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, appreciate your time, thank you.
