Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.67,0:53:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,there there's descriptions of the those states you see and what you do is you find yourself on the description of those states see is it in devotional is it experimental i mean what right now you're trying to find where to put your weight on your feet is that right
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.80,0:53:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.80,0:53:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and are you working for a firm now or what
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.80,0:53:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,um i'm looking for a job we're on a road trip to see you and
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.80,0:53:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,we're on a what
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.80,0:53:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,a road trip to see you
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.80,0:54:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and to visit grad schools and things but when i when i go back to austin i have to find my job and
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.80,0:54:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,oh i see yes i love architecture and i've done uh some of it myself i've enjoyed really enjoyed it
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.80,0:54:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,i i enjoy the creativity and the thoughtfulness and the ingenuity and projecting yourself into the space and what your life would be like if that's if you really had to be in that space and anticipate those things
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.93,0:54:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you come up with things that nobody else would think about because people don't do that
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.93,0:54:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,you know project yourself into it as to what you would be like what you would be doing what your life is like
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.89,0:54:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,here's your desk where's the bathroom you're gonna have to go the bathroom 10 times a day right where's the bathroom where's the water cooler where you know what does the what is the what is the the view from from this window etc
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.21,0:54:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,put yourself uh project yourself ahead as to actually living through what you would be doing and who you are
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.24,0:54:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and um
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.24,0:55:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that situation and then you can anticipate other things that other
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.78,0:55:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,people don't think about they're only looking at it as visual geometry in a
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.43,0:55:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,way or stylistically you know but they're not really looking at what it
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.53,0:55:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,would be to actually be there to be there you know I think architecture is
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.12,0:55:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,really wonderful it's very aesthetically pleasing creatively pleasing well can I
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.01,0:55:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,shake your hand and it's not airy-fairy it's it's for real you know yeah yes I
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.22,0:55:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,love architecture and what I used to always do is first design it from all
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.12,0:55:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,directions and then I would make a cardboard model to scale make a
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.12,0:56:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,cardboard model to scale and picture yourself as a tiny midget living there
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.34,0:56:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and you find out how hard it is to get to the stairway the way you got it
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.83,0:56:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,designed so you change it around
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.31,0:56:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you're telling him all the secrets and he's wondering boy oh yeah hello dr.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.46,0:56:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hawkins I'm Tara Carson my question is what is the best way to hold yeah I mean
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.37,0:56:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I hold another person in mind in terms of a spiritual intention I understand
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.06,0:56:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,holding it for myself but is it inappropriate to hold the hope that
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.84,0:56:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,somebody will awaken appropriate that someone else oh of course you can we did
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.48,0:56:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,it for George Soros this morning we did I held him in mind today and suddenly I
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.53,0:57:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,saw him very lovingly I saw him like a grandfather who just sort of missed the
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.73,0:57:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,boat at some turn but I didn't detract from him as an old grandfather kind of a
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.53,0:57:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,guy you know so I mean your intention and you hold that in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.79,0:57:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,then it depends on the other person's karma yeah but is it it is it through
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.26,0:57:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,prayer or intention yes yes Fereas you know we have exhibiting attention here
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.38,0:57:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's not violating their oh no because you're not forcing anything okay
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.86,0:57:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not forcing anybody I mean if George Soros goes to church Sunday
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.65,0:57:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,morning I mean it'll be on his own you know I'm not forcing you thank you yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.58,0:57:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he's going to be my hobby now.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.60,0:57:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.44,0:57:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I only heard about you from an astrologer in Illinois in October,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.12,0:58:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm from California, so I wanted to come because she said
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.10,0:58:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you were a very highly evolved spiritual being.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.20,0:58:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought, let me go and see what a highly evolved spiritual being looks like,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.82,0:58:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and I believe I have seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.34,0:58:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.14,0:58:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already signed.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.96,0:58:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I forgot to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.62,0:58:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we born at a certain caliber, or do we change throughout life as we evolve?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.88,0:58:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you constantly evolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.62,0:58:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.86,0:58:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You constantly evolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.53,0:58:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we have mechanisms like guilt and desire and disappointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.62,0:58:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all the baggage along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.34,0:58:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to see the two of you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.78,0:58:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I do hands-on energy healing, and I have a new client who is 8 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.01,0:58:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He has leukemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.07,0:58:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.55,0:58:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I spoke, 8-year-old, and I've kind of forgotten the language.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.82,0:59:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was wondering if you would have some advice for me to relate to this child,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.50,0:59:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and what can I tell him to do to help heal himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.11,0:59:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What is his function?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.08,0:59:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.66,0:59:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a leukemia patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.28,0:59:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you've got a leukemia patient, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.84,0:59:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So what advice or what information?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.84,0:59:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the patient is 8 years old?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.38,0:59:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.76,0:59:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he pray?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.54,0:59:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he go to church?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.34,0:59:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What does he do?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.66,0:59:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.96,0:59:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's all he can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.90,0:59:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.32,0:59:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Pray, go to church, be as good as he can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.96,0:59:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.04,0:59:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know, karma is karma, so what will be will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.22,0:59:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.24,0:59:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.86,0:59:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and you're writing a book on healing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.08,0:59:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Will that be out soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.40,0:59:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Next year, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.60,0:59:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.28,0:59:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.96,0:59:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's physical, mental, and spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.30,1:00:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My own medical history is disastrous, so I speak from authority.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.81,1:00:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.51,1:00:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.75,1:00:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.88,1:00:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Rachel, and I'm from New Jersey, and I'm also on a spiritual path, basically
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.10,1:00:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,by getting rid of, you know, egos, fears, and attachments, but there's one area that
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.80,1:00:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've chosen consciously not to get rid of, and that's my attachment towards my children
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.96,1:00:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and their future.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.32,1:00:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, I'm very driven to drive them, and I know that's coming from my ego, and
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.24,1:00:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm just hoping maybe you have some words of wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.08,1:00:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay to continue that attachment, and can I further along my spiritual path with
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.82,1:00:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that, or?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.46,1:00:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's see.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.56,1:00:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a partial influence, an important one, but a partial one, so you influence by
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.28,1:01:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,your choices, by what you value, because they identify with you, and I would, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.14,1:01:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,as far as trying to, I forget trying to control them, I try to attract them in that direction.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.70,1:01:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.20,1:01:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to attract them in that direction.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.14,1:01:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What direction do you want them to go?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.62,1:01:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want them to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.14,1:01:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I want my son to be like the next Stephen Hawking.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.31,1:01:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm just very driven in that way, and I know it's from an ego place.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.21,1:01:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's trying to drive them through.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.17,1:01:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.73,1:01:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, and I understand that, but I feel like I would be letting them down, and so it's
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.39,1:01:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,a dilemma within me that if I don't help them become all they can be in terms of that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.45,1:01:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.73,1:01:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.79,1:01:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So you try to give them the opportunity and follow up with supporting whatever skills
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.11,1:01:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,they exhibit in that direction, and the milieu in which they grow up greatly influences them
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.53,1:01:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,without coercion.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.55,1:02:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I grew up around music, but all my family played the piano or were musicians
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.36,1:02:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,or singers or dancers or something, you know, so I didn't have to try and control somebody.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.70,1:02:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you've got to go take lessons.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.90,1:02:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, they're in that whole milieu.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.18,1:02:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.82,1:02:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to keep them away from the piano, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.98,1:02:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.46,1:02:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.00,1:02:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, I understand what you're trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.08,1:02:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.24,1:02:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.44,1:02:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you influence them by your own interest.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.38,1:02:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't always work.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.68,1:02:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, my mother was crazy about baseball, and I always thought baseball was so boring
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.18,1:02:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't stand it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.08,1:02:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd have the dopey baseball game on.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.10,1:02:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And she'd be keeping score on all the batters, and I thought, what the hell does she see
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.98,1:02:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,in that?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.98,1:02:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.98,1:02:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.98,1:02:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.98,1:02:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Venkat.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.98,1:02:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually from India.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.98,1:03:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I've read a lot of spiritual books, starting from Paramahamsa Yogananda, Nisargadatta Maharaja,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.46,1:03:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and you know, lots of books, Eckhart Tolle as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.62,1:03:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But your books were really amazing, and they've actually changed me a lot, and I just wanted
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.38,1:03:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to thank you for your work.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.26,1:03:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.26,1:03:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.26,1:03:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for thanking me.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.26,1:03:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.26,1:03:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.26,1:03:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the Miracles book.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.29,1:03:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.29,1:03:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.29,1:03:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,With all that tape on it, you must be pretty holy by now.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.62,1:03:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And duct tape, duct tape will fix everything, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.62,1:03:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It will.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.62,1:03:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, firstly, I always like to start with I love you, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.34,1:03:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.34,1:03:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you too, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.34,1:04:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.34,1:04:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.34,1:04:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I was reading I.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.34,1:04:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.34,1:04:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.34,1:04:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The latest read is I, and it speaks of silent transmission in the grace of the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.34,1:04:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.34,1:04:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And there on the airplane yesterday, I read a description of the self, and would just
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.96,1:04:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,ask if I can hold your hand and receive that transmission.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.49,1:04:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.49,1:04:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I pass it on to you with great joy.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.49,1:04:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.49,1:04:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.49,1:04:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd like to share it with everyone in this audience.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.49,1:04:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It goes on to the eons.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.49,1:04:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.52,1:04:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.58,1:04:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Would he sign?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.58,1:04:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sign?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.42,1:04:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.10,1:04:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sign here?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.41,1:04:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.70,1:05:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe you $22,843.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.70,1:05:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.62,1:05:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.62,1:05:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you say.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.62,1:05:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a bill.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.62,1:05:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.62,1:05:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.62,1:05:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.13,1:05:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Boom.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.13,1:05:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.13,1:05:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.21,1:05:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I finished it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.63,1:05:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But first, I have a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.63,1:05:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.93,1:05:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.08,1:05:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.14,1:05:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.93,1:05:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.02,1:05:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.50,1:05:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.50,1:05:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.50,1:05:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.50,1:05:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.50,1:05:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.50,1:05:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.02,1:05:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you love for tenors.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.02,1:05:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know that you've told me that I remind you of Bocelli.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.02,1:05:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And I figured you have every Bocelli recording there is.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.02,1:05:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So I brought you three Moe tenors.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.02,1:05:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Moe tenors?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.02,1:05:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's a wonderful, wonderful presentation.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.02,1:06:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a DVD.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.02,1:06:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.02,1:06:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think you'll enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.02,1:06:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's three languages, seven different styles of music.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.02,1:06:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.02,1:06:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.02,1:06:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.02,1:06:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.02,1:06:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.02,1:06:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.02,1:06:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When I first came to Sedona in April, I gave you a copy, spiral bound copy of what I thought
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.10,1:06:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,was a pretty much finished book, except that I had the, I asked for the grace for the calibration
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.26,1:06:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to come up to the level so that other people could get a healing from it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.11,1:06:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And since that time, the book has rewritten me.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.03,1:06:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And the title's changed.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.89,1:06:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called The Struggle to Surrender.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.29,1:06:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Love, Consciousness, and the Quantum Field.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.73,1:06:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And it says inside, with deep gratitude to Sir David Hawkins, MD, PhD, whose recontextualization
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.81,1:06:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,of reality has rocked my boat and given me wings.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.20,1:06:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.20,1:07:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How very nice of you to say such a nice thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.30,1:07:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.30,1:07:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.54,1:07:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.62,1:07:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And thank you, Susan, for encouraging me to do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.78,1:07:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.78,1:07:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.70,1:07:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.98,1:07:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it propagates down through the stages.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.98,1:07:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that nice?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.48,1:07:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Very nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.48,1:07:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to you and I asked you with regards to my daughter's health if there was hope.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.49,1:07:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.49,1:07:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, I have been given so much hope.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.65,1:07:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She went from worshiping the devil.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.95,1:07:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She was an atheist and didn't think anything of taking her life for my own, and her ideal
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.59,1:07:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and her dream in life was to grow up and marry Marilyn Manson, who was a well-known Satanist.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.59,1:07:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.59,1:07:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And be a burlesque stripper.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.59,1:07:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.59,1:08:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.59,1:08:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,La, la, la.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.59,1:08:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So, as a mom, I was very devastated six months ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.59,1:08:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But since she's been here and had the prayer of the group, last week she came to me and
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.59,1:08:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,she said, I want to go to college, I want to be a therapist like Dr. Hawkins, and I
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.20,1:08:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,want to help teenage children.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.20,1:08:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said, how do you think you're going to serve them?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.20,1:08:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She goes, look at all the tools that Dr. Hawkins has given me.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.20,1:08:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She's never been left alone because she's been so unstable with her seizures.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.71,1:08:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, for the first time in her 17 years, she's apart from me, home alone in Texas.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.71,1:08:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the miraculous that I'm here, and she's experiencing a normal life without the lower
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.16,1:08:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,asterials.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.16,1:08:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And not only that, children are coming to her, and they're telling her, we're going
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.16,1:08:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to see them too, and our parents don't believe us.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.19,1:08:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's teaching them how to pray.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.19,1:08:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.19,1:08:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you taught her how to pray.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.19,1:09:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And when she says, they ask me what they can do, and I tell them to do the Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.19,1:09:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.19,1:09:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,To study Dr. Hawkins, because he is my mom's teacher, and he is my teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.19,1:09:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And even though the world's going to think you're a Branch Davidian, because they think
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.19,1:09:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,we're crazy too, you have to be very careful who you tell it to, because she tells the
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.19,1:09:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,children this.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.19,1:09:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But she says, you can come to our house, and you can pray, and we'll pray together.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.19,1:09:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And you just tell them, in the name of Jesus Christ, I refuse you, I rebuke you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.19,1:09:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So for the first time, I came to her, and I said, I'm going to leave you alone, and
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.80,1:09:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go see Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.80,1:09:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And she goes, I was waiting for you to give up this attachment of leaving me, Mom, because
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.80,1:09:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to die.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.80,1:09:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So I transcended past that.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.80,1:09:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're making great progress.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.80,1:09:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I am making such great progress.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.80,1:09:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You are too.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.22,1:09:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You are doing fine for the whole scene.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.22,1:10:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So my path today, my daughter sent me here.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.78,1:10:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She goes, you don't have to put me on my path.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.78,1:10:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm there.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.78,1:10:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, you go take care of yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.78,1:10:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So I have no questions for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.78,1:10:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I simply wanted to share my gratitude with the group, and I just wanted to know what
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.78,1:10:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,it's like to be in your presence without so much despair.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.78,1:10:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,May I just sit here for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.78,1:10:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.78,1:10:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.46,1:10:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So all turns out for the best.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.46,1:10:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.46,1:10:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Better than the best.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.94,1:10:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a little Hawkins at home that's 17 that's like spreading the word of Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.93,1:10:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She is such a devoted disciple.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.93,1:10:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.93,1:10:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.93,1:10:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank you, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.93,1:10:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that what you cherish are the principles and not the person through which you heard
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.93,1:10:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the principles.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.93,1:10:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She heard your voice above all else.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.93,1:10:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.93,1:10:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.93,1:10:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.34,1:10:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Principles above personalities.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.34,1:11:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.54,1:11:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The principles, not where you heard them from.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.89,1:11:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a phase, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.69,1:11:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.06,1:11:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.86,1:11:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.86,1:11:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.02,1:11:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.02,1:11:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.02,1:11:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to pray to you and to God in your presence for our unrelenting fixity of
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.23,1:11:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,focus.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.23,1:11:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.23,1:11:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,For our unrelenting fixity of focus to surrender every thought and emotion to God like you
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.52,1:11:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,did.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.52,1:11:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Constantly surrendering, yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.52,1:11:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.81,1:11:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the quickest way.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.81,1:11:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,As it arises, you surrender to God as it arises.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.81,1:11:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn everything over to God as it arises.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.28,1:11:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.28,1:11:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,In the beginning, it's like volitional, and then it takes up an energy of its own.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.28,1:11:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It does it of its own.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.28,1:11:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything automatically turns over.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.82,1:11:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.82,1:11:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Doc, I was just wondering if I may receive.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.82,1:11:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you called me.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.82,1:12:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.26,1:12:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.26,1:12:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.50,1:12:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.50,1:12:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.50,1:12:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.50,1:12:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.50,1:12:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.50,1:12:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.50,1:12:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.50,1:12:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.36,1:12:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.36,1:12:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.09,1:12:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.25,1:12:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.25,1:12:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.25,1:12:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.25,1:12:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.25,1:12:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.25,1:12:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.25,1:12:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.25,1:12:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You call it diksha, the transmission?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.25,1:12:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.25,1:12:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you call it diksha.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.25,1:12:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure of the correct term.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.28,1:12:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It has no term.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.28,1:12:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It has no term.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.28,1:12:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.28,1:12:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could sit before you and receive...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.28,1:12:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.44,1:12:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And plus, my intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.20,1:12:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Zap.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.20,1:12:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes down and it travels on through time, see.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.44,1:12:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.35,1:12:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Your desire for that type of energy and my desire to transmit it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.35,1:13:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it happens.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.22,1:13:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,happens. Thank you. Yeah. Yeah. Yes. Oh my God. You're going to knock me out with that if you're
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.17,1:13:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,careful. I'll pass out. I'll pass right out of here. Fall out of the chair. Yeah. Yeah. What
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.08,1:13:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you love to say is lovingness and the expression of it. Yes. All right. We'll be done by then.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.70,1:14:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be done. Yes. Just keep moving right there, honey. That's ours. Okay. That's our stack of
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.83,1:14:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,things. Is this still writing? Yes, I think it is. I just wanted to see if you could elaborate a
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.08,1:14:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,little bit on what they had first spoken about, about surrendering everything, but the yin posture
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.90,1:14:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that you had, uh, I've heard you speak about prior, um, just being there. What about it? Um,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.23,1:14:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,just elaborate on it. I, I understand. I mean, I elaborating on it. How do I elaborate?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.73,1:14:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unspeakable. I realize that, but, uh, it's a mode of being. Yeah, that's it. It's a wordless
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.76,1:15:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,mode, a style to be the receptive cup, you see, to be the receptive cup, the chalice into which
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.02,1:15:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the wisdom pours. You see, the function of the chalice is to receive divinity, you know, in
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.95,1:15:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever form.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.33,1:15:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be available at that time, symbolically wine or whatever. Yeah. Water, baptism of water,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.38,1:15:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the wine of communion, in whatever form it may exist at the time. All right. Or the fishes and
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.27,1:15:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the loaves and the fishes, in whatever way it may be proffered at the time. Amen. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.81,1:16:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.13,1:16:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.86,1:16:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A couple of years ago, I started some training in a new modality and I put things on hold while I, uh, turned my focus on to my writing and the training was with, uh, Dr. David Pesik, who is a student and disciple of Bernard Jansen on Iridology.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.25,1:16:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And Dr. Pesik calls it, uh, holistic Iridology now.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.41,1:16:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And recently, I've been turning my focus onto reading a lot of books on neuroscience.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.47,1:16:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,On what?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.79,1:16:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,On neuroscience.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.45,1:16:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.19,1:16:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was thinking of the iris as a way, as a non-invasive way to get a shortcut to looking at what paths one can take to accelerate their path to wellness.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.15,1:17:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And so my question is, is this a worthwhile direction to go?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.74,1:17:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And is it in my calling to be part of my bag of tricks?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.42,1:17:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask this.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.02,1:17:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It would serve His Highest Good to follow our ideology, resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.44,1:17:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.88,1:17:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.92,1:17:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Ben.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.50,1:17:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Ben.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.96,1:17:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's here, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.98,1:17:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to say that...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.56,1:17:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The words that you present in your teachings about the allness of divinity and its presence everywhere has changed all of our lives completely and will never be the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.48,1:17:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I made this small picture as just a tiny token of my gratitude to both of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.04,1:17:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.20,1:18:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a great gift.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.81,1:18:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a great gift.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.28,1:18:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.30,1:18:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see it?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.62,1:18:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to see it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.21,1:18:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.21,1:18:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see that well.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.78,1:18:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.96,1:18:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.66,1:18:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same as the time with light, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.37,1:18:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.63,1:18:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Bonk, bonk, bonk, bonk.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.54,1:18:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.10,1:18:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.58,1:18:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.82,1:18:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.80,1:18:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.66,1:19:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, my deepest gratitude and my love to you both for all that you have given us.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.64,1:19:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.28,1:19:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.82,1:19:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask a favor.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.92,1:19:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been very blessed to attend some of your lectures.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.98,1:19:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Where, at the end, you hold space.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.80,1:19:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You hold a vibration of love and bless us with your gazing upon us.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.38,1:19:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And that has always moved me very deeply.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.42,1:19:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And I would like to request that you do that for us at the end of our time today.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.66,1:19:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you could just take a few moments and hold that vibration of love for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.90,1:19:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.86,1:19:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.66,1:20:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, many people are attaching importance to the date, December 21st, 2012,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.82,1:20:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,similar to the harmonic convergence date in 1987.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.70,1:20:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any suggestions for what we could do at this next date
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.72,1:20:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that looks like it could be another harmonic convergence type event
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.40,1:20:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,since it seems like so many around the world will be gathering together
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.66,1:20:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to pray and meditate at the same time on that date?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.60,1:20:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That date is the next harmonic convergence.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.44,1:20:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Of that type of event.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.76,1:20:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.76,1:20:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's not mix.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.76,1:20:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not mix these things up.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.96,1:20:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Harmonic convergence is one thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.96,1:20:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Harmonic convergence is one thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.83,1:20:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,End of the world is something else.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.83,1:20:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,2012 is the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.84,1:21:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,December 21st, 2015, is the Mayan calendar, the end of a kalpa, which is a 56,000-year cycle.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.48,1:21:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.69,1:21:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the world going to come to an end at that time?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.69,1:21:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer is no.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.69,1:21:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say although it won't come to an end since so many people are gathering to pray and meditate.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.97,1:21:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not going to come to an end without the people.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.97,1:21:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They can stay home and the world's not going to come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.97,1:21:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's saying the plants are lining up again?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.90,1:21:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's something different.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.90,1:21:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The end of the world is one thing. Harmonic convergence is another.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.90,1:21:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not identical.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.90,1:21:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say just the idea that many will be gathering together
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.90,1:21:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,to pray and meditate.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.90,1:21:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's always wonderful, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.19,1:21:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't suggest kind of passing the word around
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.19,1:21:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,so more people may pray and meditate at that time?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.19,1:21:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to control things.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.07,1:22:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.25,1:22:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If the world is destined to come to an end on 2015,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.25,1:22:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,so the world comes to an end in 2015, what's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.92,1:22:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If it all ends December 21st, 2005, or 2000, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.92,1:22:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't be 2005, we'd be gone already.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.92,1:22:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,2025, 2015, doesn't make any difference.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.50,1:22:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If the world comes to an end, goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.66,1:22:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're spiritually aligned, what difference would it make
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.66,1:22:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,if it comes to an end or not?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.66,1:22:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't, that's what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.66,1:22:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to go sooner or later, so why not now?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.66,1:22:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Doc, I really appreciate that you talk about guilt.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.66,1:22:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,When you were talking about unconscious guilt,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.14,1:22:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I just realized it was like a huge flash
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.14,1:22:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that I have a lot of unconscious guilt.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.30,1:23:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I put myself in these situations where you said it'll bring up to...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.30,1:23:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, I just put myself in these weird situations.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.30,1:23:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering, how do I bring up that unconscious guilt
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.30,1:23:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to be conscious so I can clear it,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.30,1:23:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,so I don't have to put myself through these situations?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.30,1:23:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes up if you ask for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.30,1:23:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, you can do it through therapy.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.30,1:23:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, you can do it by clearing levels of energy,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.30,1:23:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and as you clear them karmically, the next level comes up.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.36,1:23:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to force it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.36,1:23:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Just your intention to clear your karma
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.36,1:23:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is enough to already start it coming up.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.36,1:23:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I feel a lot of energy in my heart chakra.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.36,1:23:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what's going on? Is that clearing?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.36,1:23:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I would guess so, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.36,1:23:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I would guess so.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.91,1:23:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.52,1:23:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget when the world's supposed to end.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.52,1:23:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,December 21st.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.00,1:23:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,2012 or 2015?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.00,1:24:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,2012.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.54,1:24:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we better pay up the mortgage, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.20,1:24:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, you won't owe anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.22,1:24:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I am 15 weeks pregnant,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.22,1:24:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and I came today...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.22,1:24:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I came today because I wanted my baby
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.22,1:24:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,to have the opportunity to be in your presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.22,1:24:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,As...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.32,1:24:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.32,1:24:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is like playing music for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.32,1:24:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.32,1:24:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like playing classical music for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.32,1:24:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So as a new mom-to-be,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.32,1:24:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,one of my concerns is autism.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.32,1:24:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was wondering what is the linear cause of autism,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.32,1:24:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and then what is the spiritual purpose of autism?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.48,1:24:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what the linear cause...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.48,1:24:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know that it falls into cause.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.48,1:24:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And I haven't kept up on the most recent research on autism,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.57,1:25:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, it's genetic predisposition and all.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.99,1:25:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can't give you anything authoritative on autism
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.99,1:25:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,from a scientific viewpoint.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.99,1:25:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If it is appropriate, would you bless the baby?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.60,1:25:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's permitted.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.15,1:25:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's permitted to bless this baby, at least.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.37,1:25:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So, by consent,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.42,1:25:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,we all bless this baby in the name of the Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.42,1:25:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.77,1:25:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.77,1:25:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.96,1:25:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That was cute.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.96,1:25:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never had...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.96,1:25:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,blessed an unborn baby yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.96,1:25:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.31,1:25:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.31,1:25:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.31,1:25:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.34,1:25:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.34,1:26:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Really grateful for your teachings.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.76,1:26:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Life is great.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.98,1:26:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.98,1:26:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The world's going to come to an end pretty soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.20,1:26:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.20,1:26:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.32,1:26:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me ask the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.32,1:26:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The world's going to come to an end on that prescribed date.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.32,1:26:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.32,1:26:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep paying the mortgage, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.22,1:26:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We've asked that over and over.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.22,1:26:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.78,1:26:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Doomsday forecasts have been recurrent throughout history.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.78,1:26:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the Book of Revelations, all of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.78,1:26:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It always calibrates as negative.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.78,1:26:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.78,1:26:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.78,1:26:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just here to thank you again for your blessings
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.78,1:26:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and express my gratitude for the love that you've given to us.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.78,1:27:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And also, I'm so glad to see all these people here
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.78,1:27:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,who I always feel good to be with.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.04,1:27:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.04,1:27:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.04,1:27:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.04,1:27:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.57,1:27:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.57,1:27:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that there's a high powerlessness
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.57,1:27:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,or lack of control over thoughts and deeds.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.57,1:27:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Over what?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.57,1:27:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thoughts and deeds.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.57,1:27:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lack of control over thoughts and deeds.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.76,1:27:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And the question is, you also said everybody's accountable for their thoughts and deeds?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.76,1:27:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.76,1:27:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.76,1:27:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You have limited control over it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.76,1:27:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.76,1:27:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You have options.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.21,1:27:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, you have the option to reject it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.88,1:27:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And let's say if somebody surrenders everything as it arises,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.88,1:27:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,then the intention itself would be surrendered.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.88,1:27:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And there would be no intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.88,1:27:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There would be no intention left.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.97,1:27:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But what would be then the karma?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.97,1:28:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's a complex question.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.32,1:28:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He's mixing things.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.32,1:28:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're mixing things.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.32,1:28:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it a simple question.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.32,1:28:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Simple.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.32,1:28:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If I give up intention,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.96,1:28:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,if I give up intention,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.96,1:28:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,like surrender everything as it arises,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.96,1:28:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.96,1:28:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,what would be the karmic consequence of the deeds that would happen?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.96,1:28:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What would be the karmic consequence of what?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.96,1:28:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Deeds.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.96,1:28:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Deeds?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.96,1:28:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.96,1:28:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Like thoughts or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.96,1:28:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thoughts or deeds?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.96,1:28:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The question doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.96,1:28:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There wouldn't be any deeds.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.72,1:28:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're giving up everything as it arises,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.72,1:28:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,there wouldn't be any consequences.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.72,1:28:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no deeds.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.72,1:28:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But the body would still do its deeds spontaneously?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.91,1:28:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What would happen?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.91,1:28:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Would the body do the deeds spontaneously?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.91,1:28:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.91,1:28:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But there would be no karmic consequences?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.91,1:28:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.36,1:28:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The animal has no karmic consequences.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.36,1:28:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Has it?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.71,1:28:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope I understand your question.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.71,1:29:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very complicated.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.71,1:29:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're presenting it, so I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.71,1:29:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.71,1:29:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Once there's no intention, there's no karma?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.06,1:29:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Once there's no intention, is there no karma?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.28,1:29:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be that broad about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.28,1:29:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a different karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.28,1:29:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a different kind of karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.28,1:29:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You might say karma comes in different flavors.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.28,1:29:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemon, lime, vanilla, chocolate, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.98,1:29:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been also asked to ask you for an OM.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.40,1:29:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They want an OM from you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.40,1:29:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,OM?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.40,1:29:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.49,1:29:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,OM who?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.49,1:29:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.49,1:29:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody wants an OM.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.49,1:29:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.88,1:29:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.88,1:29:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,About 2,500 years old.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.80,1:29:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.80,1:30:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Older than that.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.70,1:30:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.47,1:30:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we're playing.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.56,1:30:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.20,1:30:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your work.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.84,1:31:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How does one surrender spiritual ambition and willfulness and spiritual ambition?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.52,1:31:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you surrender spiritual ambition?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.00,1:31:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't surrender to the end.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.75,1:31:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Like making money, don't surrender it until you're rich.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.07,1:31:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It will come to you when spiritual ambition has become an impediment,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.45,1:31:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,when it's an expression of the spiritual ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.80,1:31:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But it requires a certain maturity
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.80,1:31:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to even contemplate the problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.19,1:31:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I wouldn't push it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.19,1:31:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, ask the Holy Spirit for an understanding of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.19,1:31:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have spiritual orientation without spiritual ambition necessarily.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.57,1:32:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Say you're talking about surrendering the spiritual ego, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.57,1:32:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You can surrender your spiritual evolution and the rate of it
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.57,1:32:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and the characteristics of it to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.57,1:32:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not difficult.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.01,1:32:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.01,1:32:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.68,1:32:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.56,1:32:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he wants to circumvent spiritual ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.56,1:32:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.11,1:32:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.11,1:32:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.11,1:32:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, precious.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.49,1:32:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.49,1:32:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to thank you for being with me always these four and a half years.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.10,1:32:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You just never have left my side through it all.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.20,1:32:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.56,1:32:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.85,1:32:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Doc, with the advent of Homo spiritus,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.85,1:33:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,is consciousness evolving another spiritual body?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.30,1:33:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I got the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.65,1:33:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, man becomes evolution.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.65,1:33:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Evolutionary development.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.65,1:33:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He develops spiritual awareness.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.65,1:33:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, the Kundalini energy comes up and activates
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.65,1:33:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the spiritual energy, yes, and then what?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.15,1:33:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the birth of a new being,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.37,1:33:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,same body, same appearance, but quite a different being.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.10,1:33:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there another spiritual body with that?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.47,1:33:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking about the etheric body?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.19,1:33:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No, like the Buddhic, Atmic.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.95,1:33:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.54,1:33:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the Buddhic body, Atmic.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.30,1:33:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, you're talking about the levels, yeah, all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.20,1:34:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, each development spiritually awakens higher chakras.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.04,1:34:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I forget how many there is above the crown chakra,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.54,1:34:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,five, seven, I forget already.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.81,1:34:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Esoteric psychology, mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.91,1:34:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.75,1:34:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I forget the names of all those
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.04,1:34:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,various spiritual bodies above the crown chakra.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.92,1:34:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.76,1:34:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.94,1:34:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.78,1:34:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.36,1:34:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to thank you for everything you've done
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.42,1:34:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and thank you for sharing between the two of you again today.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.82,1:34:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very precious to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.78,1:34:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And Susan, I wonder if you would sign those for me?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.85,1:35:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.83,1:35:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you gotta sign them?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.87,1:35:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, they're very pretty, very pretty, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.09,1:35:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.54,1:35:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are very good shots.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.98,1:35:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.44,1:35:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd like to share my gratitude for you, Susan, too,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.48,1:35:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and all your wonderful work.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.72,1:35:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in living form here and in my presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.51,1:35:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And I would like to ask if we could all speak
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.04,1:35:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Gloria in excelsis Deo together.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.88,1:35:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear what she's saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:54.18,1:35:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants us all to say Gloria in excelsis Deo.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.09,1:36:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you want us all to say it?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.64,1:36:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,In honor of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.12,1:36:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.96,1:36:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,In honor of divinity and devotion to divinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.37,1:36:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good. What?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.44,1:36:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She wanted us all to just all say it as unity.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.82,1:36:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.43,1:36:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But we'll do that at the end.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.21,1:36:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.05,1:36:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to shake everyone's hand, yeah, and everything,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.45,1:36:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,so we'll do that as a closing.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.69,1:36:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we'll do that at the end, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.39,1:36:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.23,1:36:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.46,1:36:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.87,1:36:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.58,1:36:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When you say glory to God in the highest,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.96,1:36:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,all the demons leave the room.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.71,1:36:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Any demons still hanging out?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.53,1:36:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.92,1:36:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,God, don't go in that place they're telling each other
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.48,1:36:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,all around out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.96,1:36:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go in that auditorium.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.96,1:36:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.96,1:36:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be liquefied, evaporated.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.96,1:36:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.96,1:36:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we better start shaking that now.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.96,1:36:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, you got to run faster.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.96,1:36:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak loudly and clearly into the microphone.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.96,1:36:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.96,1:36:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it all right for me to use a pendulum to test for truth?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.96,1:36:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it all right for me to what?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.96,1:36:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,To use a pendulum.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.01,1:36:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.01,1:36:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.20,1:37:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.20,1:37:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.20,1:37:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.91,1:37:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.91,1:37:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.91,1:37:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.91,1:37:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.91,1:37:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.91,1:37:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.91,1:37:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.91,1:37:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.91,1:37:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.91,1:37:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.91,1:37:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.91,1:37:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.91,1:37:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.91,1:37:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.91,1:37:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.97,1:37:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.39,1:37:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.16,1:37:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.16,1:37:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.16,1:37:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.16,1:37:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.16,1:37:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's no good.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.16,1:37:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, if you really want something that's important and you want to check, I would
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.38,1:37:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,do it with someone else.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.38,1:37:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.64,1:37:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.64,1:37:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You do little things with that.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.64,1:37:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't douse negative things to see how far down in hell you can go with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.82,1:37:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay in the positive.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.26,1:37:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.38,1:37:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay in the positive dimension, which you're going to be using that technique.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.18,1:37:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay just with that which is positive.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.08,1:37:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.33,1:37:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.33,1:37:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.33,1:37:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to get up here and thank you as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.97,1:37:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.33,1:37:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been coming down here for five years now from Toronto.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.47,1:37:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.03,1:37:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's been absolutely outstanding.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.83,1:38:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,When I attended my first lecture,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.21,1:38:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,you suggested that there would be ups and downs
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.99,1:38:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,associated with this path,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.43,1:38:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and boy, that was an understatement.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.19,1:38:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But boy, the profound changes that have happened to me
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.83,1:38:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and those within my family
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.05,1:38:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the changes that have been wrought upon me
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.59,1:38:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,have just been so amazing,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.67,1:38:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm just so incredibly grateful for being here
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.87,1:38:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and for continuing to be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.17,1:38:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we thank you, Paul, because your presence brings forth things in us
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.37,1:38:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that would not come forth were it not for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.41,1:38:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you kindly.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.25,1:38:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, we also had a chance to visit Toronto
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.27,1:38:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and go underneath the Great Falls there
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.19,1:38:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and had a wondrous time.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.21,1:38:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, and, of course, he being the sort of rascal he was,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.35,1:38:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,he got in trouble with the security guard,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.31,1:38:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and the security guard had to bring him back to us too,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.39,1:38:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,so that was a fun experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.87,1:38:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,His inner child is still active, for sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.33,1:38:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.87,1:38:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My inner child got away with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.13,1:38:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I do have one question
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.91,1:38:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,because a number of people in this lecture and others
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.29,1:39:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,have come up and asked you for the blessing or the grace
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.11,1:39:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,or the transmission and to hold your hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.49,1:39:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, is it absolutely necessary for them to do that here
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.63,1:39:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,or by actually asking silently in the audience,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.63,1:39:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,does that suffice, or should everyone come up here
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.29,1:39:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,if they so desire and ask that question?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.82,1:39:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.26,1:39:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The silent transmission does not require physicality.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.61,1:39:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.74,1:39:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Does not require physicality.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.32,1:39:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.94,1:39:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The transmission is silent,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.13,1:39:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and to merely be here already accomplishes the desired end.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.35,1:39:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.92,1:39:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.76,1:39:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The vibration of any great teacher that I visited
Dialogue: 0,1:39:52.26,1:39:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout many lifetimes
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.80,1:39:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,was already present in this lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.68,1:40:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So the advanced states that I reached at age three
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.44,1:40:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,or age 12, et cetera, which is unusual at such ages,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.30,1:40:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,was a consequence of those that I'd picked up
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.20,1:40:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,from great gurus in past lives.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.46,1:40:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.36,1:40:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.74,1:40:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I never asked that before.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.96,1:40:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.36,1:40:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.81,1:40:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So the same with this group here.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.01,1:40:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It will last throughout many lifetimes, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.67,1:40:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.33,1:40:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a permanent imprint.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.27,1:40:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.73,1:40:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.63,1:40:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you, time.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.02,1:40:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Permanent imprint.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.44,1:40:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.76,1:40:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.56,1:40:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Kiran.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.94,1:40:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from New Jersey.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.54,1:40:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I have decided to be on the spiritual path for this life.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.31,1:40:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.19,1:41:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your advice for me?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.30,1:41:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You've already chosen the spiritual path.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.48,1:41:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you pick out some teachers.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.94,1:41:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You read through some various teachers
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.90,1:41:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and see who it's.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.68,1:41:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Who attracts you, who you feel like you resonate to,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.66,1:41:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,feel familiar with, that you enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.24,1:41:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Teachers who you enjoy and who you intuit their integrity
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.42,1:41:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and that you would be willing to be devoted
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.34,1:41:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to in an ashram, let's say.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.86,1:41:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So certain figures would appeal to you, others would not.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.92,1:41:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.96,1:41:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's many karmic propensities that you cannot explain.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.32,1:41:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,See, like Ramana Maharshi would appeal to certain people.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.44,1:41:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Being a Hindu ascetic doesn't appeal to me now.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.27,1:41:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,At one time in my life, it did, and I got almost as thin as he is.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.63,1:42:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.84,1:42:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you be able to calibrate the person I'm holding in mind
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.74,1:42:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to whom I would like to devote?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.04,1:42:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:15.04,1:42:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants us to calibrate the person he's holding in mind
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.80,1:42:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,whom he would like to devote to.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.34,1:42:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who he would like to work with, or that he.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.10,1:42:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Work with, as a teacher, you mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.00,1:42:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.34,1:42:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What you really want to know is what the person you hold
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.00,1:42:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,in mind would be appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.56,1:42:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. We have permission to ask this.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.78,1:42:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher he's holding in mind would be appropriate for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:34.58,1:42:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.68,1:42:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.76,1:42:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you be able to calibrate the path?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.76,1:42:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's traditional Advaita.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.03,1:42:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.87,1:42:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.45,1:42:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we calibrate the path he's been contemplating on taking?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.15,1:42:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we already got that.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.79,1:42:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.23,1:42:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got that.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.73,1:42:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.95,1:42:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But the teacher was fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.11,1:42:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it from the list of teachers that I listed that have high-hat calibrations?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:57.41,1:42:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.05,1:42:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.59,1:42:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not the teacher in that.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.79,1:43:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.56,1:43:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So why do you pick this person?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.42,1:43:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like you said, it resonates intuitively.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.24,1:43:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.25,1:43:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So the person he's holding in mind is integrous.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.71,1:43:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.05,1:43:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.52,1:43:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He's over 400, 500, 600.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.13,1:43:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,550, 540.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.11,1:43:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,540 is unconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.41,1:43:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.41,1:43:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.41,1:43:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:30.41,1:43:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Unconditional love is a very high – unconditional love is a very high level of spiritual alignment.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.89,1:43:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I touch your feet?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.97,1:43:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.97,1:43:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.99,1:43:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.12,1:43:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.25,1:43:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.34,1:43:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless your devotion.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.34,1:43:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual level 540 is a very high level of spiritual alignment.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.34,1:43:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.34,1:43:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.90,1:43:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.90,1:44:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.13,1:44:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:02.13,1:44:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:03.13,1:44:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.13,1:44:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.13,1:44:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to thank you for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.13,1:44:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You are responsible for the recovery of millions of people on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.45,1:44:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,All the members of AA, millions of them around the globe, all as a result of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.41,1:44:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,level 540 – unconditional love, so that'll do for starters.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.39,1:44:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can cure an incurable ailment.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.36,1:44:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.36,1:44:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.36,1:44:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Scott.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.36,1:44:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from New Jersey.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.04,1:44:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had a question about music.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.86,1:44:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you've calibrated certain music in your books,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.18,1:44:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and I wanted to know if you ever calibrated
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.18,1:44:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the way the music was recorded,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.10,1:44:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,basically analog versus digitalized recordings.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.96,1:44:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.94,1:44:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I just did the music of the composer,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.63,1:44:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,not productions of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.23,1:44:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think it's possible the way music is recorded
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.27,1:44:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,could turn positive music into negative?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.81,1:45:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.61,1:45:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The music is the music of its own version.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:04.25,1:45:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So I wanted to give you an article from Dr. John Diamond,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.61,1:45:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,who wrote a paper on that.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.11,1:45:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Tintillation?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.77,1:45:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is human stress provoked by digitalized recordings.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.03,1:45:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.93,1:45:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wasn't sure if you were aware of this.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:18.67,1:45:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I wasn't aware of this.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.75,1:45:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it all right if I give it to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.59,1:45:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.69,1:45:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for your enjoyment.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.53,1:45:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the year on that that you wrote that?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:25.04,1:45:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a postscript in 2003.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.70,1:45:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,2003, there was a postscript.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.56,1:45:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It was first published in 1980.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:31.66,1:45:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.56,1:45:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I may have read it, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.52,1:45:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.02,1:45:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.52,1:45:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be glad for it, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.34,1:45:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.70,1:45:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.28,1:45:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.78,1:45:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Adarsh.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.31,1:45:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a small question.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.42,1:45:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I do two scenes.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:54.00,1:45:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said 10 times, ohm, ohm.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.18,1:45:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So will that get canceled?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.10,1:46:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, does the karma get canceled instantly?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.26,1:46:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If he does certain deeds, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:07.92,1:46:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.48,1:46:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If he does certain deeds, by saying ohm,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.30,1:46:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,would that cancel those deeds?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.74,1:46:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, cancel?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.91,1:46:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, in other words.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:18.48,1:46:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.10,1:46:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, bad karma, good karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.78,1:46:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, say, if he did a bad deed,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.82,1:46:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,would saying ohm, would that cancel?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.42,1:46:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.04,1:46:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not going to change it, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.00,1:46:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be like graffiti in Lourdes Cathedral.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.84,1:46:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So what would he do if he did a bad deed?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:46.36,1:46:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What would he do to cancel that bad deed?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:48.12,1:46:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:48.70,1:46:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In remorse?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.94,1:46:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.62,1:46:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You regret.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.58,1:46:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You ask for forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.64,1:46:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And you go on and do good deeds to cancel it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.01,1:47:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone has done things that they wish they had not done.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.41,1:47:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.27,1:47:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we weren't born perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:06.01,1:47:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we were born perfect, if we were perfect,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.97,1:47:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,we wouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.89,1:47:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.33,1:47:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And one more is, why do we forget our past births?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.29,1:47:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do we forget our past lives?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.85,1:47:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:20.35,1:47:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If we remember all that we .
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.23,1:47:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not within one's present sense of reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.23,1:47:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go into an older state of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.61,1:47:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and go back into a previous lifetime just like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.29,1:47:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And I could explain more about it, but it's too involved.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:37.49,1:47:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What you presume to be the center of your importance
Dialogue: 0,1:47:41.71,1:47:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,right now is where you focus.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:44.90,1:47:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If in a different circumstance what you were at other times
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.78,1:47:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is more important, then you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.82,1:47:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance, you can go to the whatchamacallit Institute
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.80,1:47:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,in the East Coast.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.61,1:48:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:00.11,1:48:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go to the Monroe Institute and learn
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.43,1:48:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,various techniques to go out of body and visit previous lifetimes
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.73,1:48:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.67,1:48:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's quite intriguing.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.79,1:48:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And sometimes you learn things that are useful and sometimes
Dialogue: 0,1:48:12.37,1:48:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,not.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.52,1:48:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I learned about my negative karma with horses
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.50,1:48:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.00,1:48:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I touch your feet?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:22.20,1:48:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And I forgave the horses and I forgave myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.44,1:48:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And now we're fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.32,1:48:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:27.20,1:48:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:28.88,1:48:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.76,1:48:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:30.26,1:48:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.52,1:48:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to learn all these cameras.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.28,1:48:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.78,1:48:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.57,1:48:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.07,1:48:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, hello, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:53.39,1:48:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.27,1:48:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:55.73,1:48:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Bharat, and we are all from New Jersey.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.01,1:49:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.51,1:49:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:02.01,1:49:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:02.51,1:49:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Just last.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:03.01,1:49:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Just last.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:03.51,1:49:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Just last.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:05.01,1:49:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Just last.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.96,1:49:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We have been on the spiritual path for a year now.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.73,1:49:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:10.53,1:49:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.03,1:49:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We have been on the spiritual path for a year
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.87,1:49:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,now, and we just got introduced to you
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.47,1:49:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,through my cousin and your teachings.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.37,1:49:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And we just got introduced to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.97,1:49:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're here to take your blessings.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.34,1:49:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.84,1:49:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We would like to touch your teeth and bless.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:23.86,1:49:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please bless us to grow at a higher spiritual level.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:26.60,1:49:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:27.10,1:49:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a beautiful family to bless.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:28.60,1:49:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you all in the name of the Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:30.98,1:49:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.57,1:49:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to touch your feet?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.95,1:49:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.73,1:49:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The very, I see very yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:39.01,1:49:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.41,1:49:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.01,1:49:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.51,1:49:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:43.75,1:49:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:44.41,1:49:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The act of devotion.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:44.99,1:49:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Devotion in itself is a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:48.46,1:49:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're already blessed by your intention, your tradition.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:57.74,1:50:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher in India is that of the guru,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:00.10,1:50:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and different than American or Western styles.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.68,1:50:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an act of commitment and intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:14.20,1:50:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:18.25,1:50:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for your devotion and faith.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:20.49,1:50:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.51,1:50:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:30.27,1:50:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:31.39,1:50:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:32.35,1:50:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Kind of.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:32.99,1:50:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.90,1:50:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So we need some music to conclude with, and we promised we were going to do something at
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.12,1:50:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the end.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:46.12,1:50:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to shake hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.12,1:50:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, first we're going to bless the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:50.88,1:50:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:51.88,1:50:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to do the silence prayer, and then you guys shake hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:53.01,1:50:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to do what?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.01,1:50:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to do the blessing of the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:55.01,1:50:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:56.01,1:50:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:57.01,1:50:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.01,1:50:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:59.01,1:51:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.01,1:51:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:01.49,1:51:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:02.49,1:51:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:03.49,1:51:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.49,1:51:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:05.49,1:51:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:06.49,1:51:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:43.44,1:51:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:44.44,1:51:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Blessed we are now and forevermore.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:50.17,1:51:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Blessed we are to be with each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:56.19,1:52:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You are my blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.00,1:52:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We are each other's blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:01.26,1:52:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Through us, the energy of divinity sweeps through mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:14.16,1:52:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:17.01,1:52:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,By being together, we serve God, our fellow man, and also our higher self through acts
Dialogue: 0,1:52:37.90,1:52:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,of devotion in one.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:39.44,1:52:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And we thank You, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:46.70,1:52:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:47.96,1:53:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,blessing of those present through eternity. Come in together, and we leave together. We stay united,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.96,1:53:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,united by our love and our devotion, and I do bless you all in the name of the Lord,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.12,1:55:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Almighty God, now and forever. Amen. Amen. Sparks of the one, and we all collectively indeed,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:31.12,1:55:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and so we love each other now and forever. Amen. Thank you so much. The blessing of your
Dialogue: 0,1:55:45.96,1:56:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,presence. So in this moment passes all of time. Having transcended time, we are no longer
Dialogue: 0,1:56:46.95,1:56:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,subject to it. Thank you, Lord. Until I see you next. Amen.
